Angel Prime/Starwind/Blade Runner/Depth Charge/Steed/Rattrap


Rattrap fire two shots taking out both missles fired from Unicron.


Angel Prime tried to fly out of the way but 2 shots hit his arm giving 
him a nasty burn look. he then fired a small firebolt at Unicron. 
Before the firebolt hit him it formed a fire bubble around Unicron 
slowly moving in. Starwind fire all the front lasers from his gun 
ports. Rattrap fired 25 rapid shots. Steed fired ten plasma charges. 
All of them went into the fireball then it exploded with Unicron in 
the middle.


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Blade Runner threw random fireballs at Sun Crusher and Dark Wulf.


~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Depth Charge fired two Ion disks at Sun Crusher.
